  1003                                  ; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
  1004                                  ;**	System file table entry
  1005                                  ;
  1006                                  ;	These are the structures which are at SFTABLE in the SF structure.
  1007                                  ; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
  1008                                  
