  8582                                  ;**	$Set_Interrupt_Vector - Set Interrupt Vector
  8583                                  ;---------------------------------------------------
  8584                                  ;	$Set_Interrupt_Vector is the official way for user pgms to set the
  8585                                  ;	contents of an interrupt vector.
  8586                                  ;
  8587                                  ;	M004, M068: Also set A20OFF_COUNT to 1 if EXECA20OFF bit has been set 
