 27563                                  ; NOTE: Secondary (Buffer) Cache is not used in PCDOS 7.1 IBMDOS.COM
 27564                                  
 27565                                  ; (Win ME IO.SYS - BIOSCODE:BB93h)
 27566                                  ; (MSDOS 6.22 IO.SYS - DOSCODE:7C0Eh)
