 31790                                  ; Procedure Name : MakeNode
 31791                                  ;
 31792                                  ; Inputs:
 31793                                  ;       AL - attribute to create
 31794                                  ;       AH = 0 if it is ok to truncate a file already by this name
 31795                                  ;	AH != 0 if truncation not allowed (prexisting file is an error)
 31796                                  ;               (AH ignored on dirs and devices)
 31797                                  ;
 31798                                  ;        NOTE: When making a DIR or volume ID, AH need not be set since
 31799                                  ;               a name already existant is ALWAYS an error in these cases.
 31800                                  ;
 31801                                  ;       [WFP_START] Points to WFP string ("d:/" must be first 3 chars, NUL
 31802                                  ;               terminated)
 31803                                  ;       [CURR_DIR_END] Points to end of Current dir part of string
 31804                                  ;               ( = -1 if current dir not involved, else
 31805                                  ;                Points to first char after last "/" of current dir part)
 31806                                  ;       [THISCDS] Points to CDS being used
 31807                                  ;       [THISSFT] Points to an empty SFT. EXCEPT sf_mode filled in.
 31808                                  ; Function:
 31809                                  ;       Make a new node
 31810                                  ; Outputs:
 31811                                  ;       Sets EXTERR_LOCUS = errLOC_Disk or errLOC_Unk via GetPathNoset
 31812                                  ;       CARRY SET IF ERROR
 31813                                  ;          AX = 1 A node by this name exists and is a directory
 31814                                  ;          AX = 2 A new node could not be created
 31815                                  ;          AX = 3 A node by this name exists and is a disk file
 31816                                  ;               (AH was NZ on input)
 31817                                  ;          AX = 4 Bad Path
 31818                                  ;               SI return from GetPath maintained
 31819                                  ;          AX = 5 Attribute mismatch
 31820                                  ;          AX = 6 Sharing Violation
 31821                                  ;               (INT 24 generated ALWAYS since create is always compat mode
 31822                                  ;          AX = 7 file not found for Extended Open (not exists and fails)
 31823                                  ;       ELSE
 31824                                  ;          AX = 0 Disk Node
 31825                                  ;          AX = 3 Device Node (error in some cases)
 31826                                  ;          [DIRSTART],[DIRSEC],[CLUSFAC],[CLUSNUM] set to directory
 31827                                  ;               containing new node.
 31828                                  ;          [CURBUF+2]:BX Points to entry
 31829                                  ;          [CURBUF+2]:SI Points to entry.dir_first
 31830                                  ;          [THISSFT] is filled in
 31831                                  ;               sf_mode = unchanged.
 31832                                  ;          Attribute byte in entry is input AL
 31833                                  ; DS preserved, others destroyed
