 34810                                  ; Character type table for file name scanning
 34811                                  ; Table provides a mapping of characters to validity bits.
 34812                                  ; Four bits are provided for each character. Values 7Dh and above
 34813                                  ; have all bits set, so that part of the table is chopped off, and
 34814                                  ; the translation routine is responsible for screening these values.
 34815                                  ; The bit values are defined in DOSSYM.INC
 34816                                  
