 42011                                  ;	Coalesce adds the block following the argument to the argument block,
 42012                                  ;	iff it's free.  Coalesce is usually used to join free blocks, but
 42013                                  ;	some callers (such as $setblock) use it to join a free block to it's
 42014                                  ;	preceeding allocated block.
