 43517                                  ;**	SFFromSFN - Get an SF Table entry from an SFN
 43518                                  ;----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 43519                                  ;	SFFromSfn uses an SFN to index an entry into the SF table. This
 43520                                  ;	is more than just a simple index instruction because the SF table
 43521                                  ;	can be made up of multiple pieces chained together. We follow the
 43522                                  ;	chain to the right piece and then do the index operation.
 43523                                  ;
 43524                                  ;   NOTE:
