 45621                                  ;BREAK <TransPath - copy a path, do string sub and put in current dir>
 45622                                  ;----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 45623                                  ;
 45624                                  ;   TransPath - copy a path from DS:SI to ES:DI, performing component string
 45625                                  ;       substitution, insertion of current directory and fixing . and ..
 45626                                  ;       entries. Perform splicing. Allow input string to match splice
 45627                                  ;       exactly.
 45628                                  ;
 45629                                  ;   TransPathSet - Same as above except No splicing is performed if input path
 45630                                  ;       matches splice.
 45631                                  ;
 45632                                  ;   TransPathNoSet - No splicing/local using is performed at all.
 45633                                  ;
 45634                                  ;   The following anomalous behaviour is required:
 45635                                  ;
 45636                                  ;       Drive letters on devices are ignored. (set up DummyCDS)
 45637                                  ;       Paths on devices are ignored. (truncate to 0-length)
 45638                                  ;       Raw net I/O sets ThisCDS => NULL.
 45639                                  ;       fSharing => dummyCDS and no subst/splice. Only canonicalize.
 45640                                  ;
 45641                                  ;   Other behaviour:
 45642                                  ;
 45643                                  ;       ThisCDS set up.
 45644                                  ;       FatRead done on local CDS.
 45645                                  ;       ValidateCDS done on local CDS.
 45646                                  ;
 45647                                  ;   Brief flowchart:
 45648                                  ;
 45649                                  ;       if fSharing then
 45650                                  ;           set up DummyCDS (ThisCDS)
 45651                                  ;           canonicalize (sets cMeta)
 45652                                  ;           splice
 45653                                  ;           fatRead
 45654                                  ;           return
 45655                                  ;       if \\ or d:\\ lead then
 45656                                  ;           set up null CDS (ThisCDS)
 45657                                  ;           canonicalize (sets cMeta)
 45658                                  ;           return
 45659                                  ;       if device then
 45660                                  ;           set up dummyCDS (ThisCDS)
 45661                                  ;           canonicalize (sets cMeta)
 45662                                  ;           return
 45663                                  ;       if file then
 45664                                  ;           getCDS (sets (ThisCDS) from name)
 45665                                  ;           validateCDS (may reset current dir)
 45666                                  ;           Copy current dir
 45667                                  ;           canonicalize (set cMeta)
 45668                                  ;           splice
 45669                                  ;           generate correct CDS (ThisCDS)
 45670                                  ;           if local then
 45671                                  ;               fatread
 45672                                  ;           return
 45673                                  ;
 45674                                  ;   Inputs:     DS:SI - point to ASCIZ string path
 45675                                  ;               DI - point to buffer in DOSDATA
 45676                                  ;   Outputs:    Carry Set - invalid path specification: too many .., bad
 45677                                  ;                   syntax, etc. or user FAILed to I 24.
 45678                                  ;               WFP_Start - points to beginning of buffer
 45679                                  ;               Curr_Dir_End - points to end of current dir in path
 45680                                  ;               DS - DOSDATA
