 48243                                  ;   ShareEnd - terminate sharing info on a particular SFT/UID/PID. This does
 48244                                  ;       NOT perform a close, it merely asserts that the sharing information
 48245                                  ;       for the SFT/UID/PID may be safely released.
 48246                                  ;
