 52489                                  ; Retro DOS v4.0 NOTE: (by Erdogan Tan, 25/04/2019)
 52490                                  ; ----------------------------------------------------------
 52491                                  ; This data section which was named as uninitialized data
 52492                                  ; (as overlayed by initialization code) but follows 
 52493                                  ; initialized data section from DOSDATA:03B6h address
 52494                                  ; (in otherwords, the method is different than MSDOS 3.3,
 52495                                  ; and there is not overlaying..)
 52496                                  ; **********************************************************
 52497                                  ; Reference: MSDOS 6.21 kernel DOSDATA section (4970 bytes)
 52498                                  ; follows DOSCODE section in the kernel file (MSDOS.SYS) 
 52499                                  ; (it is located at offset 0BF70h, file offset 0BF70h-3DE0h) 
 52500                                  ; but starts from offset 0 (ORG 0) and ends at offset 1370h.
 52501                                  ; TIMEBUF is at offset 03B6h.
